{"tid":2480370,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"做左10年室內設計，你問我答 (3)","createTime":"2021-04-08T12:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:20:59.000Z","uid":74177,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f79f96a5018b6c1f978ba27802cf35534f4e35","tid":2480370,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"又係我開post la <br />\n雖然上個post少左人問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我都會堅持答落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有平面圖俾我，我都會盡答你既！<br />\n為左可以問到所有巴打問題，請咁多位巴打對平面圖有問題直接TG我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇覆你答你既話請炸下我催下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">上個post有條撚樣屈我同好師傅有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係度再講多次，本人無同好師傅有任何關係我連掛單都無啊DLLM!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我叫你地睇下野咋仆街！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.codeco.hk/zh-tw/renovation101/tags/%E7%89%A9%E6%96%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.codeco.hk%2Fzh-tw%2Frenovation101%2Ftags%2F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%2596%2599%2F&d=VcdoNmHqL8UCHTV4lpGTbYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=347214b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.codeco.hk/zh-tw/renovation101/tags/%E7%89%A9%E6%96%99/</a><br />\n <img src=\"https://s3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/com.codeco-hk.cms/editor/190522093622/2018_12_18_custom_furniture_966x503a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcom.codeco-hk.cms%2Feditor%2F190522093622%2F2018_12_18_custom_furniture_966x503a.jpg&h=8d1d0b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY8Q5e8ciL5yY881gkLPamqvdZyEGFicrU9uiTikC19de?filename=9WafRM9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WafRM9.jpg&h=27efb86a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/com.codeco-hk.cms/editor/190522083234/2019_02_27_kitchen_panel_966x503a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcom.codeco-hk.cms%2Feditor%2F190522083234%2F2019_02_27_kitchen_panel_966x503a.jpg&h=d6210961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/com.codeco-hk.cms/editor/200313234220/2018_08_31_tile_materials_966x503a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcom.codeco-hk.cms%2Feditor%2F200313234220%2F2018_08_31_tile_materials_966x503a.png&h=342c7744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/com.codeco-hk.cms/editor/191030144530/2019-10-30_BH_3-Door.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcom.codeco-hk.cms%2Feditor%2F191030144530%2F2019-10-30_BH_3-Door.jpg&h=3004ba80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d7ed850d2a678af67ee1554185f669972373404","tid":2480370,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"我發現都幾多學生會睇我個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔敢講我可以教到你地好多野，我都唔係大學出身唔識太多野<br />\n但你地有野問我都會答你地既<br />\n我綜合咁多學生既問題有呢幾個<br />\n<br />\n1. 人工高唔高?<br />\n其實唔好諗會賺大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫餓你唔死有份工咖姐<br />\n細公司入職11-13K<br />\n大公司16K左右<br />\n<br />\n2. 點樣先可以進步D? 同D同學既差距好大?<br />\n睇多D 畫多D 練習多D<br />\n我讀書個陣就會睇下D雜誌 e.g. perspective magazine <br />\n係我讀書既3年俾到好多資訊我<br />\n仲有一樣我到依加都會成日做既就係行多D街，行多D商場<br />\n其他商場好多野睇好多野學，特別係一D名店既window display<br />\n行個陣可以留意下D window display，天花既結構，地下唔同材料既駁口<br />\n仲有就係唔好睇D咩室內設計技巧書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇就睇多D平面設計既書籍，你可以學既野會更加多，同埋仲可以更加你既對美感既睇法<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他我諗到先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我開左個grp，希望可以幫到同既同學仔係讀書既時候有咩難題都有個照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGroup chat : <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/TMBzBFMUyCwX3z4f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FTMBzBFMUyCwX3z4f&d=VcdoNmHqL8UCHTV4lpGTbYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=4b4a45b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/TMBzBFMUyCwX3z4f</a>"},{"pid":"48764d9160f2b739b4c28912c6201f40e04da2c0","tid":2480370,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68342f896e482c9676fd2bc780132391cb4ddb3","tid":2480370,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48764d9160f2b739b4c28912c6201f40e04da2c0","tid":2480370,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935babf2e2ad66cda4defcec3bf25cc17cf0121e","tid":2480370,"uid":252091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"有無响人哋間屋屌個閪？"},{"pid":"4c665b4eaac37a504052f6c12deb3b9603987616","tid":2480370,"uid":74177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"935babf2e2ad66cda4defcec3bf25cc17cf0121e","tid":2480370,"uid":252091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"有無响人哋間屋屌個閪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成地水泥沙咁